<p><strong>Add the cross-compilation target locally:</strong><br>
</p>

<div class="highlight js-code-highlight">
<pre class="highlight shell"><code>rustup target add aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu
</code></pre>
<div class="highlight__panel js-actions-panel">
