<p>The <code>proxy_set_header</code> lines are worth understanding. <code>Host $host</code> passes the original domain name to the app. <code>X-Real-IP $remote_addr</code> passes the real client IP address. Without these, your app would see all requests as coming from <code>127.0.0.1</code>, which makes logging and debugging harder.</p>

